Fix indentation inconsistency with https_wrapper

This file used 2 space indentation instead of 4 like the rest of the
project. It actually caused me to write a bug that took a second to
figure out.
Ran
```
$ autopep8 ~/src/duo_client_python/duo_client/https_wrapper.py --select=E101,E121 --in-place
```
